page.title: 17 Oxford St. Area
page.content: The people in our area are quite friendly. There are a few shops. Most of the people work in these shops. Those who live in this area think that it is a very safe place to walk at night. The street has many fine examples of Georgian and Regency houses and buildings.In the last few years the residents and business owners have got together to run a street_market.One of the oldest shops in the street has been supplying uniforms to officers in the Army ,Navy and Air_force for about 200 years now.
